{
  "stem": "93.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he finally came to the conclusion that maybe I was going to shoot him, and he moved away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when he moved away, the crowd broke up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we went through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we passed through Jena, and we came to Gera.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes, it was Gera.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got on the Autobahn that led to Dresden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at some point, it was going to intersect the Autobahn that went to-- to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Here, we ran into another really horrible sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Autobahn was a natural route for people to walk and try to get east, because it was all well-grated, and all that sort of stuff.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what had happened is the German unit which we were following-- or chasing, basically-- had seen these people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were literally thousands of them walking down the Autobahn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as they came by, they machine gunned them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was just 40 or 50 armored vehicles, presumably.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, I don't know the exact number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But assuming-- assuming that there was a fair number of vehicles, they all turned their guns on these people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so as we came by, there were hundreds-- hundreds of people-- women, children, men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Without regard to anything, they had just simply machine gunned them, because these people had these black and white uniforms on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Shortly after that, we got to a German town called Oberleimbach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Oberleimbach.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The reason I remember it is because the GIs very quickly dubbed it 'Oh My Lame Back,' which was a favorite expression with the GIs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And at that point-- this is now very late April, perhaps early May-- we received orders to evacuate, which was a good part of East Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
